# CppCoreGuidelines.md:5261
msgid "5261    ### <a name=\"Rh-ptr-cast\"></a>C.148: Use `dynamic_cast` to a pointer type when failure to find the required class is considered a valid alternative"
msgstr""

       
# CppCoreGuidelines.md:5262
msgid "5262    ##### Reason"
msgstr""

       
