# CppCoreGuidelines.md:5361
msgid "5361    Overload rule summary:"
msgstr""

       
# CppCoreGuidelines.md:5362
msgid "5362    * [C.160: Define operators primarily to mimic conventional usage](#Ro-conventional)"
