msgstr""

# CppCoreGuidelines.md:10801
msgid "10801    This quickly becomes unmanageable."
msgstr""

# CppCoreGuidelines.md:10802
msgid "10802    Alternatively, we can add a `try`-`catch` to `use()` to map `Z` into an acceptable exception."
