# CppCoreGuidelines.md:13905
msgid "13905    ### <a name=\"Rl-camel\"></a>NL.10: Prefer `underscore_style` names"
msgstr""

       
# CppCoreGuidelines.md:13906
msgid "13906    ##### Reason"
msgstr""

       
# CppCoreGuidelines.md:13907
